00:41:42,370 --> 00:41:46,670
She can lie really well and will bite when she's angry.

505
00:41:46,670 --> 00:41:48,500
You should be careful too, Brother.

506
00:41:48,500 --> 00:41:51,350
As I told you, I am not your brother.

507
00:41:54,330 --> 00:41:56,280
Let's have a talk.

508
00:41:57,150 --> 00:41:59,340
I've nothing to say to you.

509
00:42:03,030 --> 00:42:05,790
"Break down the seven walls

510
00:42:08,160 --> 00:42:10,800
and gather in Ham Joo."

511
00:42:30,320 --> 00:42:32,190
Lady.

512
00:42:38,240 --> 00:42:40,960
Lady. I'm up here.

513
00:42:44,640 --> 00:42:47,980
Oh, sir! What are you doing up there?!

514
00:42:49,830 --> 00:42:51,980
I'm doing first level training.

515
00:42:51,980 --> 00:42:56,990
First level. As you may know, I'm not someone who should be doing first level training, right?

516
00:42:56,990 --> 00:42:58,810
Right?

517
00:43:00,170 --> 00:43:04,220
Still, you have to start from the bottom and slowly take your chances.

518
00:43:04,220 --> 00:43:06,390
Hurry and go back to your position. Understand?

519
00:43:06,390 --> 00:43:07,670
Then.

520
00:43:08,490 --> 00:43:11,120
Lady— Lady!

521
00:43:14,900 --> 00:43:17,120
This isn't it...

522
00:43:17,120 --> 00:43:22,060
You said I was best.... 
I almost fell off.

523
00:43:37,750 --> 00:43:39,620
Ahjussi.

524
00:43:48,780 --> 00:43:51,320
Even though I'm not sure,

525
00:43:51,320 --> 00:43:58,750
you already know that much. Now, you called me out here, defenseless, to a quiet place. What's next?

526
00:43:58,750 --> 00:44:00,130
Who is it?

527
00:44:00,130 --> 00:44:04,030
Who is on top of this and leading your organization?

528
00:44:04,030 --> 00:44:06,750
 Lee Shin Jeok 

529
00:44:06,750 --> 00:44:10,780
If I get caught, I would bite my tongue off here and die.

530
00:44:10,780 --> 00:44:13,430
Whatever you try, that person is-—

531
00:44:13,430 --> 00:44:16,790
Father wants to meet that person.

532
00:44:17,910 --> 00:44:22,010
For what that organization is doing, don't they need Father?

533
00:44:22,010 --> 00:44:25,420
Then why didn't they pass the An Byeon Chaek?

534
00:44:25,420 --> 00:44:28,000
 An Byeon Chaek: A plan to stabilize the border 

535
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:31,190
General knows about it too?

536
00:44:31,190 --> 00:44:36,050
Yes and he wants to meet that person.

537
00:44:36,910 --> 00:44:41,210
 Tonight at Ja Shi, the place is at the memorial shrine of Hong Yoon Myo.
 (Ja Shi: Between 11pm and 1am)  

538
00:44:41,210 --> 00:44:46,460
 You and that person. My father and I. Just four people. Everyone should be unarmed. 

539
00:44:46,460 --> 00:44:49,480
 Please keep that promise. 

540
00:44:50,320 --> 00:44:52,070
Pardon?!

541
00:44:52,070 --> 00:44:56,080
You said General really wants to meet that person?

542
00:44:56,080 --> 00:45:00,900
Yes! Finally, the General is getting involved!

543
00:45:00,900 --> 00:45:02,730
I'm lying.

544
00:45:04,670 --> 00:45:07,710
Father never said that.

545
00:45:10,760 --> 00:45:12,510
Young Master, are you insane?

546
00:45:12,510 --> 00:45:14,280
Why would you do that?

547
00:45:14,280 --> 00:45:19,120
Father is like a mountain,

548
00:45:19,120 --> 00:45:21,610
and this is something that requires moving a mountain.

549
00:45:23,220 --> 00:45:25,950
I'll meet that person before him.

550
00:45:25,950 --> 00:45:30,140
Then, with that person, I will move a mountain.

551
00:45:31,960 --> 00:45:35,870
I'll do that, for sure.

552
00:45:40,860 --> 00:45:42,610
I've met him.

553
00:45:42,610 --> 00:45:44,190
Thank you for helping me out.

554
00:45:44,190 --> 00:45:46,600
Okay. What did he decide to do?

555
00:45:46,600 --> 00:45:51,160
Ajussi said to use me as a messenger.

556
00:45:54,150 --> 00:45:56,020
'Ajussi'?

557
00:45:57,070 --> 00:45:59,080
Never mind.

558
00:45:59,080 --> 00:46:01,040
Read it.

559
00:46:01,040 --> 00:46:02,960
It's okay for me read to you?

560
00:46:02,960 --> 00:46:05,850
Bon Won said that

561
00:46:05,850 --> 00:46:11,780
he trusts you, so I guess I will do that too from now on.

562
00:46:20,910 --> 00:46:26,490
If General Lee Seong Gye's reaction to the An Byeon Chaek is like that, then I will personally—

563
00:46:29,650 --> 00:46:34,310
I'll meet Lee Seong Gye in person.

564
00:46:34,310 --> 00:46:38,850
It's difficult but make it possible.

565
00:46:38,850 --> 00:46:41,000
Does Bon Won think that way as well?

566
00:46:41,000 --> 00:46:45,030
But will the General meet him?

567
00:46:46,640 --> 00:46:49,920
Actually, it's already been arranged.

568
00:46:49,920 --> 00:46:54,010
I heard that General Lee Seong Gye wants to meet that person himself.

569
00:46:54,010 --> 00:46:58,510
Oh. That's good then even if I'm not sure.

570
00:47:00,780 --> 00:47:04,600
That side proposed it first?

571
00:47:04,600 --> 00:47:06,230
They know about our organization?

572
00:47:06,230 --> 00:47:09,790
That's why they asked to arranged this meeting.

573
00:47:11,180 --> 00:47:15,330
Sure, I'll get going now.

574
00:47:20,040 --> 00:47:23,630
But what if it's a trap?

575
00:47:26,070 --> 00:47:31,440
General Lee is not someone who would do that.

576
00:47:31,440 --> 00:47:33,870
Yes.

577
00:47:33,870 --> 00:47:37,660
I know it isn't my place,

578
00:47:37,660 --> 00:47:44,140
but in this world I grew up in, there's no such thing
 as "that kind of person, not that kind of person".

579
00:48:02,630 --> 00:48:03,950
Right there.

580
00:48:03,950 --> 00:48:05,870
We decided to meet there.

581
00:48:05,870 --> 00:48:08,280
I'll wait right here.

582
00:48:08,280 --> 00:48:13,420
If General Lee Seong Gye shows up, I'll go to Ajussi and let him know.

583
00:48:18,540 --> 00:48:23,100
If anything strange happens outside, immediately blow on this thing.

584
00:48:23,100 --> 00:48:24,610
Yes.

585
00:48:32,970 --> 00:48:35,460
Are you really alright?

586
00:48:35,460 --> 00:48:38,670
Will he really come out?

587
00:48:39,590 --> 00:48:41,430
What if it's a trap?

588
00:48:41,430 --> 00:48:45,960
Stay here and watch. If needed, you must come running right away.

589
00:48:45,960 --> 00:48:50,060
I would be running, but...

590
00:48:53,070 --> 00:48:57,390
Ah, really, can he really do this without the General's permission?

591
00:49:13,980 --> 00:49:19,190
Please, please be there, you must be there.

592
00:49:26,360 --> 00:49:28,710
Why are you alone?

593
00:49:28,710 --> 00:49:31,540
Why did you come alone then?

594
00:49:31,540 --> 00:49:32,990
He will come soon.

595
00:49:32,990 --> 00:49:35,820
That person will come soon too.

596
00:49:35,820 --> 00:49:39,510
It's past the promised time, how?

597
00:49:39,510 --> 00:49:44,520
You didn't lie to me so that I would bring him to you?

598
00:49:53,100 --> 00:49:54,600
 It was a trap! 

599
00:49:54,600 --> 00:49:56,310
It isn't a lie.

600
00:49:56,310 --> 00:50:00,930
We decided that I would greet him first and then meet my father.

601
00:50:00,930 --> 00:50:02,550
If you wait a bit more...

602
00:50:02,550 --> 00:50:06,340
So it was a trap. Lee Bang Won.

603
00:50:25,740 --> 00:50:29,040
 Darn it. I knew this would happen. 

604
00:50:48,560 --> 00:50:49,700
Young Master.

605
00:50:49,700 --> 00:50:51,660
Ahjussi!

606
00:50:55,640 --> 00:50:57,230
Ahjussi!

607
00:51:00,310 --> 00:51:03,050
Ahjussi, there's a huge problem!

608
00:51:03,050 --> 00:51:05,960
  General, General, General! 

609
00:51:05,960 --> 00:51:08,630
Wait, what's the ruckus?

610
00:51:11,150 --> 00:51:15,750
Just now, Young Master Bang Won got kidnapped.

611
00:51:17,040 --> 00:51:18,490
What are you talking about?

612
00:51:18,490 --> 00:51:20,790
How did he get kidnapped?

613
00:51:20,790 --> 00:51:25,440
Bang Won? How is that he is here?

614
00:51:25,440 --> 00:51:27,200
Um, that..

615
00:51:27,200 --> 00:51:28,740
Just spit it out!

616
00:51:28,740 --> 00:51:33,070
I'll tell you everything.

617
00:51:40,150 --> 00:51:43,750
Aiyo. Was it wrong to come here?

618
00:51:45,590 --> 00:51:48,030
Shouldn't I just have caught the Viper?

619
00:52:02,340 --> 00:52:03,950
What should I do with this person?

620
00:52:03,950 --> 00:52:08,840
He is injured. It's too much to drag two people with us.

621
00:52:09,760 --> 00:52:11,480
Just kill him.

622
00:52:25,250 --> 00:52:27,210
What are you guys?

623
00:52:57,350 --> 00:53:00,600
Hurry and escape. It's Bon Won's order.

624
00:53:00,600 --> 00:53:02,010
What are you talking about?

625
00:53:02,010 --> 00:53:05,800
Please come out for a little bit. I have something to tell you.

626
00:53:32,490 --> 00:53:33,900
What are you talking about?

627
00:53:33,900 --> 00:53:36,570
I have a servant protecting me.

628
00:53:36,570 --> 00:53:39,530
I saved you again.

629
00:53:39,530 --> 00:53:41,840
It must be our fate.

630
00:53:41,840 --> 00:53:44,210
Please be quiet.

631
00:53:46,550 --> 00:53:49,280
My servant has probably reported everything.

632
00:53:49,280 --> 00:53:53,830
He probably misunderstood that I got kidnapped.

633
00:53:53,830 --> 00:53:56,780
The soldiers have probably already been mobilized.

634
00:53:57,450 --> 00:54:00,440
Leave me, go ahead and block it.

635
00:54:00,440 --> 00:54:02,290
Tell them that I am safe and it's all a misunderstanding.

636
00:54:02,290 --> 00:54:08,060
If he's already reported everything, then my identity must have already been found out. Do you think they will believe me?

637
00:54:08,060 --> 00:54:11,220
You should be the one to stop it. Go!

638
00:54:11,220 --> 00:54:15,110
You. Can you run while carrying me on your back?

639
00:54:15,790 --> 00:54:18,380
Me? Why?

640
00:54:21,560 --> 00:54:23,060
  Bang Won! 

641
00:54:23,780 --> 00:54:25,720
Young Master!

642
00:54:27,850 --> 00:54:30,430
I will slit this wench's throat.

643
00:54:36,780 --> 00:54:42,760
Between you wenches, I already know that there is a secret organization.

644
00:54:43,850 --> 00:54:50,470
I also know that those bastards kidnapped our young master.

645
00:54:51,780 --> 00:54:54,230
It's not me. It's really not me!

646
00:54:54,230 --> 00:54:56,310
Confess.

647
00:54:57,890 --> 00:55:00,040
Where is he?

648
00:55:00,040 --> 00:55:02,100
Tell me!

649
00:55:07,170 --> 00:55:11,170
If not, your neck will be separated from your head.

650
00:55:17,950 --> 00:55:20,580
You guys are going to stay quiet?

651
00:55:24,890 --> 00:55:30,780
Then, I will cut this wench's head off first and ask again.

652
00:55:30,780 --> 00:55:32,850
  Stop, stop! 

653
00:55:32,850 --> 00:55:36,130
  Stop, stop! 

654
00:55:36,130 --> 00:55:38,490
Stop, stop!

655
00:55:39,420 --> 00:55:41,300
He wasn't kidnapped.

656
00:55:41,300 --> 00:55:43,300
We've found Bang Won!

657
00:55:43,300 --> 00:55:45,110
He's safe.

658
00:55:51,320 --> 00:55:52,900
But!

659
00:55:52,900 --> 00:55:57,600
It is true that you have bad intentions for coming into Ham Joo.

660
00:55:59,310 --> 00:56:01,050
General.

661
00:56:02,100 --> 00:56:04,370
I will take this opportunity to fish out that organization

662
00:56:04,370 --> 00:56:07,890
so it doesn't happen again.

663
00:56:16,050 --> 00:56:21,330
All the things you told me, are they all just lies?

664
00:56:22,420 --> 00:56:28,180
About your village's people dying and about that young girl, Uh Nyeon's death,

665
00:56:28,180 --> 00:56:30,920
and the tears you have shed.

666
00:56:31,720 --> 00:56:35,790
No, It isn't a lie.

667
00:56:35,790 --> 00:56:40,990
It's not just me. The homeless people who gathered here in Ham Joo for the past years

668
00:56:40,990 --> 00:56:43,910
are all the same.

669
00:56:43,910 --> 00:56:49,280
In this whole land of Goryeo, I only have my small self.

670
00:56:49,280 --> 00:56:52,440
That's why I came here. It's the truth.

671
00:56:54,430 --> 00:56:59,490
If not for you taking us in, all of us

672
00:56:59,490 --> 00:57:04,750
are just people who would be corpses rotting on the walkways.

673
00:57:06,560 --> 00:57:08,410
The reason why that person

674
00:57:09,290 --> 00:57:17,030
sent us to you, General, is because our despair, hopes,

675
00:57:17,030 --> 00:57:20,470
and dreams will be accepted.

676
00:57:21,440 --> 00:57:26,520
I think that is the meaning of being saved in this world.

677
00:57:27,440 --> 00:57:31,170
Then who is it?

678
00:57:37,050 --> 00:57:41,710
Reveal everything. General is asking.

679
00:57:46,380 --> 00:57:48,500
That person...

680
00:58:01,160 --> 00:58:02,750
That person...

681
00:58:03,510 --> 00:58:05,660
  Right here. 

682
00:58:19,060 --> 00:58:21,940
I am that person.

683
00:58:21,940 --> 00:58:23,970
Ahjussi..

684
00:58:23,970 --> 00:58:26,120
Ahjussi?

685
00:58:34,590 --> 00:58:37,270
  That, that person..! 

686
00:58:38,920 --> 00:58:42,230
 War should not be decided by those who have power! 

687
00:58:42,230 --> 00:58:45,860
 It's not something that can be decided by old people. 

688
00:58:48,440 --> 00:58:51,490
 That man is the Jantgar. 

689
00:58:51,490 --> 00:58:53,790
 Jantgar: Strongest man 

690
00:58:55,770 --> 00:59:01,500
 The owner of the New Joseon is Jangpyeong Gate's Jantgar. 

691
00:59:05,270 --> 00:59:08,930
It's me. Jeong Do Jeon.

692
00:59:08,930 --> 00:59:17,070
 Timing and Subtitles brought to you by
The Flying Dragons Team at Viki.com 

