00:59:24,170 --> 00:59:25,740
Six Flying Dragons

694
00:59:25,740 --> 00:59:29,370
 Do you think I will waver because of one word from a scholar I just met? 

695
00:59:29,370 --> 00:59:31,890
 - He's a person we can trust.
- I will not do it. 

696
00:59:31,950 --> 00:59:34,620
 I'm asking you why you called Lee Seong Gye to block my path. 

697
00:59:34,620 --> 00:59:35,860
 I'm thinking of helping you. 

698
00:59:35,860 --> 00:59:37,020
 What exactly are you saying? 

699
00:59:37,020 --> 00:59:39,540
 I need you, Brother, and you also need me. 

700
00:59:39,540 --> 00:59:41,360
 What are you? What are you doing? 

701
00:59:41,360 --> 00:59:45,430
 - Why is it me?
- I'm going to defeat those three people and establish a new country. 

702
00:59:45,430 --> 00:59:48,540
  I chose you. 

